# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
coverage
*.local

# Postgres bind mount in dev — `docker-compose.yml` mounts
# `${DATA_DIR:-./data}/postgres` into the postgres container.
# Without DATA_DIR exported (the prod `deploy.sh` sets it to
# `$HOME/data/nodea`), local dev falls back to `./data/postgres`
# at the repo root. Never commit dev DB state.
# Anchored to the repo root (`/data/`) on purpose: an unanchored
# `data/` also swallowed source dirs like
# `packages/web/.../Account/views/data/`.
/data/

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?

# Claude Code — local harness state (scheduled-task locks, agent
# transcripts, etc.). Per-machine, never committed.
.claude/

# Secrets — single canonical location at the repo root, written by
# the Dev Setup VS Code extension from Infisical (see `dev-setup.yaml`).
.env

# Test environment overrides — points DATABASE_URL at the dedicated
# `nodea_test` database so `pnpm test` doesn't TRUNCATE the dev rows.
# See packages/api/vitest.config.ts. Created by `pnpm db:setup-test`.
.env.test

# Misc
export.md
/dev-setup.yaml